      "role": "user",
      "content": "We are adding some AI-based tools for fraud detection. It’s pretty cool, like the app can now predict risky transactions. Oh, and the movie I was talking about is called \"Dil Bechara\" — it's based on a popular novel. Have you heard of it?"
