      "role": "user",
      "content": "The story is emotional but beautiful, inspired by a real-life love story. The actors did a great job — their chemistry was \"unbelievable\" (aapke liye \"unbelievable\" ka use sahi hai?). But let me ask you, do you watch Bollywood movies?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Yes, I watch Bollywood movies! You used 'unbelievable' perfectly — it fits well there. What character did you connect with most in Dil Bechara?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hmm, it's hard to pick just one character — both main characters are so \"kayi\". But maybe the male lead, he's very loyal and kind. I think most people can relate to him. Anyway, I should get back to work. Talk to you later, Maya!"
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Got it, small tweak: \"kayi\" is a Hindi word — we’d say \"relatable\" or \"real\" in English. The male lead sounds inspiring. Tell me how the work meeting went later!"
